debug

Class DebugWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • venicehub.VeniceWriter
      • debug.DebugWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class DebugWriter
extends VeniceWriter
    A debugging implementation of VeniceWriter. It just prints TTE strings to console.

    It takes TTE items from TTEQueue, converts them via XIOParser into a string and print it to console. With setQuiet the printing can be suppressed.
